                      votes <span class="ItemCaption">Reviewed: </span>
                      <span>2004-04-24</span>
                    </div>
                    <span>As a new person on the Wall Street, I picked this book after reading all reviews instead of Hull as my first book.<p>Reviews said undergraduates can handle this book. Wrong. Despite solid engineering background (IIT), I found this to be rather dry book. Certaily not the first book.<p>I have started Hull. And found that much more accessible and practically useful. Gets you into solving problems and getting answers.</span>
                  
              
